---
title: Parmesan Caesar Chicken Burgers with Tomato-Spinach Salad
description: Spend less time in the kitchen and more time with your family! The star ingredient of these easy burgers is Parmesan. It combines with minced chicken and breadcrumbs to make a flavourful patty that's tucked between artisan buns with baby spinach and Caesar dressing.
